Package eu.diversify.trio.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SystemPart
    Common interface of every sub part of the system
    SystemVisitor
    Ability to traverse a system
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Component
    A component is an entity of the system, whose status might be active or inactive depending on others component's status.
    DefaultSystemVisitor
    Ability to traverse a system, following the containment relationships.
    Dispatcher
    Dispatch visit events (i.e., enter, exit) to other visitors, to factor out the cost of traversing large models.
    Evaluation
    Iterate through the sub parts of a system and notifies the associated listener of the progress.
    System
    Represent the specification of a system under study.
    Tag
    A 'tag' used to classify the components of the system
